- I will jump again.

00:28:38.390 --> 00:28:43.185
Unfortunately, I can play
the whole thing, so--

00:28:43.185 --> 00:28:46.470
I'm going to go a few sections.

00:28:50.204 --> 00:28:53.697
[WIND WHISTLING]

00:30:42.480 --> 00:30:43.169
- The very end.

